window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A Mysterious Island. Unbridled Lust. The Adventure of a Lifetime.</b></p> <p>After ten years together, Jeremy “Jem” Creed and his wife, Crystal, are looking to give their marriage a fresh start on Paradeisos, a mysterious island off the coast of Oregon. What they find is stranger than they could have imagined: the locals are named after Greek gods, horned thugs lurk in back alleys, and the women are strangely friendly.</p> <p>An anonymous message from something called Erebos opens Jem's life to new possibilities, including a local rock star named Ruby Inke. But Ruby comes with secrets that make her as dangerous as she is beautiful.</p> <p>Can Jem and Crystal unravel the mysteries on the island before they find themselves lost in paradise?</p> <p><i>Masters of Reality</i> is a steamy harem mystery that has the MC and his wife bringing another woman into their marriage. The sex scenes are explicit. Welcome to a unique experience from Aaron Crash, the bestselling author of the American Dragons and the Princesses of the Ironbound series.</p>"; 
